                "text": "All policies, procedures and guidelines will be approved by the Infection Prevention and Control Committee for each site,  which are the specialist  groups  with  the authority  to  approve  IPC  Policies  These  will  then  be  forwarded  to  the Document  control  team  for  submission  and  ratification  by  the  Joint  Document Management Group."
